member.summary:
Returns all commands that are registered in the command system.
	The data returned adheres to the following layout:
	```
	[
		{
			"name": "cmdlist"
		},
		{
			"name": "command1"
		}
	]
	```

Returns all commands that are registered in the command system.
The data returned adheres to the following layout:
```
[
{
"name": "cmdlist"
},
{
"name": "command1"
}
]
```
